When love beckons to you, follow him,

Though his ways are hard and steep.

And when his wings enfold you yield to him,

Though the sword hidden among his pinions may wound you.

And when he speaks to you believe in him,

Though his voice may shatter your dreams as the north wind lays waste the garden.

For even as love crowns you so shall he crucify you. Even as he is for your growth so is he for your pruning.

Even as he ascends to your height and caresses your tenderest branches that quiver in the sun,

So shall he descend to your roots and shake them in their clinging to the earth.

Like sheaves of corn he gathers you unto himself.

He threshes you to make you naked.

He sifts you to free you from your husks.

He grinds you to whiteness.

He kneads you until you are pliant;

And then he assigns you to his sacred fire, that you may become sacred bread for God’s sacred feast.

All these things shall love do unto you that you may know the secrets of your heart, and in that knowledge become a fragment of Life’s heart.

But if in your fear you would seek only love’s peace and love’s pleasure,

Then it is better for you that you cover your nakedness and pass out of love’s threshing-floor,

One day she met a boy named Trev on a rainy day wearing black cloak Lily was wet in the rain the boy asked her to come under her umbrella. They started talking about each other on their way home. She told the boy that no one likes her and she is lonely. The boy asked her to come with him in his magic world. He gave her headphones. She wore it and they both held each other's hand. They were in the *DIFFERENT WORLD* where everything was opposite from Earth. It was a fantasy world. The boy was a sorcerer he made a beautiful world with his superior magic where no one can come. Their stories were same, they fell in love. They did many adventures. The girl wanted to go back on Earth for some time to meet her father. The boy let her go she promised him that she will come back here soon. She got to know that her father loves her very much. She stayed with him till his death. After her father's funeral she again started feeling lonely. She wore the headphones and came back to the boy's world. But nothing was same the colourful world was destroyed. Everything went dark and black. A boy was standing there in black hoodie and mask his name was Alan. He told the girl that the boy was a bad sorcerer, he lost his parents and after his sacrifices he became superior. But he did crimes so he was punished by a good witch. He can't control his body. The witch said that he will be only freed when someone like you starts loving you. His powers will be taken away from him and he will rebron on Earth to proof that he's good. He had ignited when she has gone and he took rebirth after few months in a good family. Now he has to proof himself. Lily said, "Again I lost my loved one. Why always me? So many sacrifices...." Alan gave her a mask and asked her to come with him in the Walker World. She met many good people. She enjoyed the adventures. But after 20 years she is still waiting for that boy when she is 36. Maybe they will meet again and that love story will continue. Ofcourse they will meet.\n\nSorry for my bad english. And I didn't think much about the story when I was writing it. comment_text:
“Diamond Heart” is a demo/reference track by singer-songwriter Sia.

The song was conceived in late 2017 when she was working with David Guetta on his 2018 album 7.

She wrote the foundations as an un-credited songwriter on the song, “Say My Name”, where she met Thomas Troelsen. In those sessions they also worked on “Diamond Heart” which was rejected by Guetta.

They then pitched the song to Alan Walker, who reproduced it with Mood Melodies and Jesper Borgen, got Sophia Somajo to record vocals and released it as the final single of his World Of Walker single trilogy in September, 2018.
Name: Diamond_Heart

comment_text:
I think this is actually a movie made from 7 songs and not just a Triology. Here is what I think:-

Part 1:-
1.Sing me to Sleep: Some person or entity guides a Group of people together. They form a group called Walkers. They carry an object in their backpack that when united projects a pattern on the ceiling. 

Alone: All Walkers feel lonely so the main Walker ( we will call him Alan) puts out a call on the internet  to Walkers from all around the World to Unite and see that they are not alone. 

Tired: Many years after the forming of the Walkers, a Solar Flare approaches fast. Groups of Walkers form devices that would scan ruins and once united construct a Utopia for Survivors of Flare. They bury them underground where they will be safe and wait for the Flare to hit and them Presumable die. 
End of Part one.

Part 2:-
Faded: One of the Walkers who survives is trying to cope up with the new world after the Flare. He's completely alone and trying to find a place that's not in ruins because of the Flare, guided by the picture of a lovely rural house. He travels a long way hoping that this house would be his salvation. But when he gets there he is disappointed to see that it is destroyed like everything else.

End of Part Two

Part 3:-
All Falls Down: An unknown amount of time later a group of teenagers, who presumably grew up in the post apocalyptic world, dig up one of the safes with the scanners, but don't know what to do with it. In night a Group of older people, Presumabley some of the Walkers who buried the scanners in the first place, come and set up something that shows them how to use the scanners. 

Darkside: The group of older Walkers are scanning a monument of some sort and the teenagers watch them doing it afar. They are inspired and after fiddling with the scanners a bit, go and scan other monuments. Finally both the groups of Walkers meet on the Mountain top. 

Diamond Heart: Different groups of Walkers discover these Scanners and their use, and soon the sheild starts showing what the other Walkers are scanning. The scanners proceed to guide the Walkers together and finally they build their Utopia.
This is true or false. Maybe what I wrote was not good or what. But this is what I thought.
Name: Diamond_Heart
